[hduser@mn2 ~]$
[hduser@mn2 ~]$
[hduser@mn2 ~]$ exit
logout
Connection to mn2 closed.


From machine(192.168.1.10), we are able to make the communictaion without password.

[hduser@mn1 .ssh]$ chmod 600 id_rsa.pub authorized_keys

